      <title>奥特曼支持的核电公司将使用西门子电力系统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/nuclear-developer-backed-by-altman-to-use-siemens-power-system</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Oklo Inc. 是一家由亿万富翁萨姆·奥特曼 (Sam Altman) 支持的先进核反应堆开发商，该公司同意在其发电厂中使用西门子能源的组件，此举旨在加速其技术的部署。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/nuclear-developer-backed-by-altman-to-use-siemens-power-system</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 13:30:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
